<div class="impactStatistics">
<div class="container">
<div class="impactStatistics__content bg-purple-20">
<div class="eyebrow">OUR IMPACT</div>
<h4 class="impactStatistics__header">Inspiring parents to lock up their guns at home</h4>
<div class="d-lg-flex">
<div class="font-statistic-large impactStatistics__number">5x</div>
<div class="d-lg-flex flex-lg-column impactStatistics__right">
<p class="font-large impactStatistics__statisticEnding">About 4.6M children live in homes with an unsecured firearm, contributing to tragedies. But gun-owning parents who see our End Family Fire ads are over 5x more likely to seek information about safe storage.</p>
<a class="font-medium impactStatistics__source" href="https://bradyunited.org/programs/combating-crime-guns">Source</a>
</div>
</div>
<a class="bbtn bbtn--large impactStatistics__cta" href="https://bradyunited.org/about-us/our-impact">See Our Impact</a>
